------------------------------------------
DYNAPHOPY 1.0
------------------------------------------
Program to calculate crystal anharmonic frequencies from molecular
dynamics calculation obtained from VASP code.

------------------------------------
Installation instructions
------------------------------------
1. Requisites
Python 2.6 or higher
Matplotlib
Scipy
Phonopy

2. Download the source code a put it in the installation directory

3. Run the setupy script
python setup.py install --home=.

